## Get Up and Running in 5 Minutes

```bash
# Clone and start the stack
git clone https://github.com/The-Abhishek1/XCLOAK-SECURITY-SUITE.git
cd XCLOAK-SECURITY-SUITE && docker compose up -d

# Start the backend
cd xcloak-ngfw/backend
cp .env.example .env && go run ./main.go

# Open the dashboard
open http://localhost:3000
```

First signup creates the admin account. 43 Sigma rules are seeded automatically. Your first agent can be enrolled in under a minute.

[Full Deployment Guide →](https://docs.xcloak.tech/deployment)

---

## Deploy to Kubernetes

```bash
helm install xcloak charts/xcloak \
  --namespace xcloak --create-namespace \
  --set global.ingress.host=xcloak.yourdomain.com \
  --set backend.env.JWT_SECRET=$(openssl rand -hex 32)
```

[Helm Chart Reference →](https://docs.xcloak.tech/deployment/helm)

