## Open-Core Model

XCloak's backend, agents, and mobile app are open-source under the Business Source License 1.1. The license converts to Apache 2.0 in 2029.

The Next.js frontend dashboard is proprietary (open-core). If you are interested in access to the frontend source, contact abhishekn1003@gmail.com.

